<FlowDocument xmlns="http://schemas.microsoft.com/winfx/2006/xaml/presentation"
              ColumnWidth="400" FontSize="30" FontFamily="宋体"
              Foreground="Black">
    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="36">定义：</Run>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="30">在做加法时，如果一个加数接近整十、整百、整千......，可以先把它看做整十、整百、整千......进行运算，然后再加上少加的数，或减去多加的数。</Run>
        <LineBreak />
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="30">如果两个加数分别为a、b，且b=m×10±n（m、n为正整数），则</Run>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="30">a+b=a+(m×10±n)</Run>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="30">   =(a+m×10)±n</Run>
    </Paragraph>

    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="32">举例：</Run>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="28">578+397=?</Run>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="28" Foreground="Black">解答：</Run>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="24" Foreground="Black"> 578+397</Run>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="24" Foreground="Black">=578+400-3</Run>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="24" Foreground="Black">=978-3</Run>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="24" Foreground="Black">=975</Run>
    </Paragraph>
</FlowDocument>
